room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by I Escaped Memphis in Memphis
room_description: A new museum exhibition is in town showcasing a multi-million dollar Faberge Egg and you're planning to steal it. You and your group are sneaking in after hours. You will have to get the codes, solve the puzzles from the art gallery, and not to mention having to navigate through a laser trap to get to your prize. Your task is to get to the egg and get the code to escape the room in 60 minutes. Be careful, it won't be easy!
